dc_title_s: Wildebeest Observations: Athi-Kapiti Plains, Kenya, 1977-78 and 1994-96
dc_description_s: This polygon shapefile portrays number of wildebeest observed in 1977-78 and 1994-96 in the Athi-Kapiti Plains, Kenya. Note: This data shows numbers of wildebeest observed during the wet season by low-altitude flights. The data was then aggregated to 5km grid cells by number observed.This data was used in Map 5.15 in Nature's Benefits in Kenya: An Atlas of Ecosystems and Human Well-Being.
